content.rendered:
Roll dressings consist of a highly absorbent inner, enclosed in a soft and comfortable non-woven fabric. The roll can be cut to sizes that suit.

Suitable For:

  • Moderate exudating wounds
  • Padding or protection for major wounds
  • Primary or secondary dressing

Product Features:

  • Soft and comfortable
  • Low linting
  • Cut to size
  • Highly absorbent
